Titolo: Marvel Puzzle Quest

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Marvel Puzzle Quest is a video game released by D3 Publisher and Marvel Entertainment on October 3, 2013, and developed by Demiurge Studios. The fourth installment in the Puzzle Quest series, it is a free-to-play, match-three Bejeweled-style puzzle battle game set in the Marvel universe, featuring 254 playable, unlockable, recruitable Marvel characters.It is available for free on the App Store for iOS, Google Play for Android and Steam for Microsoft Windows. A high-definition port of the game developed by WayForward Technologies was released on PlayStation 3, PlayStation 4, and Xbox 360 in 2015; and Xbox One in 2016. The game was released on Amazon Kindle in 2016.